{"tid":1548240,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"明報今報：無第8個","createTime":"2019-09-07T03:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T12:48:58.000Z","uid":268927,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"64785e9b4ede52f3687fd4376b5edafe9d9f6d3b","tid":1548240,"uid":268927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:14:15.000Z","msg":"明報特稿<br />\n【明報專訊】8‧31太子站速龍警員衝入港鐵車廂打人事件，「打死人」以至「毁屍滅迹」傳言不斷，昨更引發巿民集結太子站，要求港鐵公開閉路電視片段。當局稱當日傷者均以港鐵專列由太子站送到荔枝角站B2出口上救護車，本報翻看荔枝角站B2出口外的閉路電視片段，查證當晚經該出口離開的傷者共7人，人數與消防處公布脗合，當中有人以繃帶包頭、躺在擔架牀上不見動彈，亦有人雙手疑被綁。有當晚被捕者及目擊者計劃透過法律途徑，要求港鐵交出太子站閉路電視片段。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20190907/s00001/1567794967195/%e7%89%b9%e7%a8%bf-cctv%e7%89%87%e8%ad%898-31%e4%b8%83%e5%82%b7%e8%80%85%e8%8d%94%e6%9e%9d%e8%a7%92%e9%80%81%e9%99%a2-%e8%a2%ab%e6%8d%95%e8%80%85%e7%9b%ae%e6%93%8a%e8%80%85%e6%93%ac%e5%be%aa%e6%b3%95%e5%be%8b%e7%a8%8b%e5%ba%8f-%e7%b4%a2%e5%a4%aa%e5%ad%90%e7%ab%99%e7%89%87%e6%ae%b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190907%2Fs00001%2F1567794967195%2F%25e7%2589%25b9%25e7%25a8%25bf-cctv%25e7%2589%2587%25e8%25ad%25898-31%25e4%25b8%2583%25e5%2582%25b7%25e8%2580%2585%25e8%258d%2594%25e6%259e%259d%25e8%25a7%2592%25e9%2580%2581%25e9%2599%25a2-%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258d%2595%25e8%2580%2585%25e7%259b%25ae%25e6%2593%258a%25e8%2580%2585%25e6%2593%25ac%25e5%25be%25aa%25e6%25b3%2595%25e5%25be%258b%25e7%25a8%258b%25e5%25ba%258f-%25e7%25b4%25a2%25e5%25a4%25aa%25e5%25ad%2590%25e7%25ab%2599%25e7%2589%2587%25e6%25ae%25b5&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAT632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=934a74bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190907%2Fs00001%2F1567794967195%2F%25e7%2589%25b9%25e7%25a8%25bf-cctv%25e7%2589%2587%25e8%25ad%25898-31%25e4%25b8%2583%25e5%2582%25b7%25e8%2580%2585%25e8%258d%2594%25e6%259e%259d%25e8%25a7%2592%25e9%2